  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Patients with a complete drug allergy work-up to betalactam antibiotics were contacted (by
      mail) and asked to answer a questionnaire regarding the tolerance upon readministration of a
      negatively tested beta-lactam.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
